Jubilee Holdings of Kenya Unit Is Granted Fund-Manager License

-- B y   E r i c   O m b o k
-- 
2011-07-08T05:23:58Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-08/jubilee-holdings-of-kenya-unit-is-granted-fund-manager-license.html
Jubilee Holdings Ltd. (JBIC) ’s, a Kenyan
insurer, received a license to operate as a fund manager, the
Capital Markets Authority said.  “The grant of a license to Jubilee Financial Services Ltd.
brings the number of fund managers licensed by the Authority for
the year 2011 to 20,” the Nairobi-based industry regulator on
its  website .  Jubilee Financial Services is a wholly owned subsidiary of
Jubilee Holdings, which is listed on the  Nairobi Stock Exchange ,
Dar es Salaam Stock Exchange and Uganda Securities Exchange.
Jubilee Holdings has insurance operations in Kenya, Uganda,
Tanzania and last year established a presence in Burundi and
Mauritius.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Eric Ombok in Nairobi at 
 eombok@bloomberg.net .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Shaji Mathew at 
 shajimathew@bloomberg.net . 